steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"9dkj4","text":"The arabidopsis seeds are immersed with 50% bleach in 1.5 µL tubes.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"2h51a","text":"Gently remove the supernatant and leave the seeds in the tube.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"41m3","text":"The sterile seeds are immersed in distilled water.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
